{"id":"api/core/HostListener","title":"HostListener","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/HostListener\", \"name\": \"HostListener\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1096-L1096\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"hostlistener\">HostListener<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#hostlistener\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8jwiiwcvk99qcng5hm98g8mtl\">一个装饰器，用于声明要监听的 DOM 事件，并提供在该事件发生时要运行的处理器方法。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/HostListener#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<section class=\"decorator-overview\">\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table option-overview\">\n  <thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th>选项</th>\n    <th>说明</th>\n  </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e69fj4rn5feqfay1llax24xfj\"><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#eventName\"> <code>eventName?</code> </a></td>\n      <td>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1arcz3y0i2umuev2bale1cdd0\">要监听的事件。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3gijha1btxiry1uvepg76lbri\"><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#args\"> <code>args?</code> </a></td>\n      <td>\n\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e5nmr8hozbr9j9abb47r0y0rg\">当该事件发生时传给处理器方法的一组参数。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  \n</section>\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"byr9v7au06fba8088348xa0cc\">当宿主元素发出指定的事件时，Angular 会调用提供的处理程序方法，并使用结果更新绑定元素。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b5tpm0cldo5d349z9hhmxhzdj\">如果处理程序方法返回 false，则在绑定元素上应用 <code>preventDefault</code>。</p>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3pby4i5loovy42dhei4tjia83\">更多信息请参阅\n<a href=\"api/core/HostListener#usage-notes\">使用说明...</a></p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">选项<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  \n  <a id=\"eventName\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>\n          <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n            <h3 id=\"eventname\">eventName<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#eventname\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n            <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1020-L1023\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n          </div>\n        </th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1arcz3y0i2umuev2bale1cdd0\">要监听的事件。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n            eventName?: string\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n  \n  \n  <a id=\"args\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>\n          <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n            <h3 id=\"args\">args<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#args\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n            <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1024-L1027\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n          </div>\n        </th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e5nmr8hozbr9j9abb47r0y0rg\">当该事件发生时传给处理器方法的一组参数。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n            args?: string[]\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n  \n</section>\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostListener#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4ouiti82bi25oim7p45f0ykun\">下面的例子声明了一个指令，它会为按钮附加一个 <code>click</code> 监听器，并统计点击次数。</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: 'button[counting]'})\nclass CountClicks {\n  numberOfClicks = 0;\n\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostListener</a>('click', ['$event.target'])\n  onClick(btn) {\n    console.log('button', btn, 'number of clicks:', this.numberOfClicks++);\n  }\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app',\n  template: '&lt;button counting&gt;Increment&lt;/button&gt;',\n})\nclass App {}\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"etrl5ua46ys00r21ftuskeydm\">以下示例注册了另一个 DOM 事件处理程序，它会侦听全局 <code>window</code> 上的 <code>Enter</code> 按键事件。</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nimport { <a href=\"api/core/HostListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostListener</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a> } from \"@angular/core\";\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app',\n  template: `&lt;h1&gt;Hello, you have pressed enter {{counter}} number of times!&lt;/h1&gt; Press enter key\nto increment the counter.\n  &lt;button (click)=\"resetCounter()\"&gt;Reset Counter&lt;/button&gt;`\n})\nclass AppComponent {\n  counter = 0;\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostListener</a>('window:keydown.enter', ['$event'])\n  handleKeyDown(event: KeyboardEvent) {\n    this.counter++;\n  }\n  resetCounter() {\n    this.counter = 0;\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5aogerk9u0w6mokhq9hdm8lxk\">可以在此处找到 <code>keydown</code> 和 <code>keyup</code> 事件的有效键名列表：https: <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events-key/#named-key-attribute-values\">//www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events-key/#named-key-attribute-values</a></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9gsiakmujrsk8724hqk3gkpzy\">请注意，键也可以组合，例如 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/HostListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostListener</a>('keydown.shift.a')</code>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"gf8a4gxmg1jets204jqw7tva\">可用于事件名称前缀的全局目标名称是 <code>document:</code> 、 <code>window:</code> 和 <code>body:</code>。</p>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - guide/attribute-directives\n - guide/change-detection-skipping-subtrees\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/dependency-injection-in-action\n - guide/styleguide\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/HostListener#args\n - api/core/HostListener#description\n - api/core/HostListener#eventName\n - api/core/HostListener#eventname\n - api/core/HostListener#hostlistener\n - api/core/HostListener#options\n - api/core/HostListener#usage-notes\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1020-L1023\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1024-L1027\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L1096-L1096\n - https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events-key/#named-key-attribute-values\n-->"}